    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNo \"ghost text\" like suggestion from history when typing command or search pattern. Like in `fish` / `nu` shell or ['Sam-programs/cmdline-hl.nvim' plugin](https://github.com/Sam-programs/cmdline-hl.nvim). The one is inserted after manually pressing `<Up>`, but interactively shown one can be useful as a reference.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nAutomatically show as \"ghost text\" the latest history entry that matches currently typed text.",
